creator: 1 Step Garage
descriptionHtml:
Your car stopped working? Looking for spare parts for your car? Finding the nearest detailer? Want to call for a winch? 1 step Garage helps you in finding the best service provider for all your automobile needs. We provide a platform to connect consumers directly to the service provider.
As a customer you can filter out your search on the bases of your need and area. This helps you find the right person in no time. You can also enquire about spare parts and services you need through the application, along with getting exclusive offer. If you get stuck, you can call winch to help take the car to the garage.
As a business owner, this is a great platform for you to reach out to more customers. You can build your profile. If you register your spare parts shop you can receive enquire requests directly from customers. Along with all this you can also view the number of shares and visits to your profile
descriptionShort: We aim to build an easy bridge between customer and automobile service provider.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: New features (My Car) full database for each user to maintain and schedule all their car needs. You can add repair, maintenance and upgrade records of your car. You can also email all the data from the app to your registered email.
